'''Dust fever''' was an illness common among children on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The afflicted individual often had vivid dreams—and rarely lucid dreams—of strange and unusual themes.{{Talesstart}} 

[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] was prone to dust fever. In [[9 BBY/Legends|9 BBY]]. he contracted a case of the disease while attempting to run away from [[Lars homestead/Legends|home]] during a [[Sandstorm/Legends|sandstorm.]] During his illness, he had a [[Force vision/Legends|vision]] of a menacing [[Anakin Skywalker|dark figure]] standing over him. 

A boy called "[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Annie]]" helped him survive the storm and Luke was also able to kill a [[Krayt dragon/Legends|Krayt dragon]] with a [[gaderffii stick|gaderffiii stick]] that the pair had taken from the body of a [[Tusken Raider|tusken raider]]. However, when his [[Owen Lars/Legends|Uncle Owen]] and other searchers found Luke, there was no sign of the other boy or the dragon and they passed the experience off as a dust fever dream, though Luke insisted that it was real.{{Talesend}}

